<i>But most people are
thinking about heading home.</i>

30:45.340 --> 30:47.108
<i>Have you ever been tempted</i>

30:47.110 --> 30:48.676
<i>to hang around for the winter?</i>

30:48.678 --> 30:50.111
No.

31:23.578 --> 31:26.313
<i>When the last plane leaves
that's it.</i>

31:26.315 --> 31:28.716
<i>You're stuck here
for the next 6 months.</i>

