32:18.702 --> 32:20.735
<i>you're my family
for the next 6 months. "</i>

32:22.805 --> 32:24.739
<i>My first season
was in the winter</i>

32:24.741 --> 32:26.608
<i>and I do recall watching</i>

32:26.610 --> 32:28.477
that last plane leaving
and thinking

32:28.479 --> 32:31.113
boy I hope this is
what I want to do.

