<i>During the summer,</i>

34:40.245 --> 34:42.911
<i>it's only a 10-minute
helicopter flight away.</i>

34:42.914 --> 34:45.380
<i>But during the winter
it means getting in a vehicle,</i>

34:45.382 --> 34:48.484
<i>like a Pisten Bully
and driving there.</i>

34:48.485 --> 34:51.454
<i>When conditions are good
it's about a six-hour drive.</i>

34:51.456 --> 34:53.956
<i>But in recent years
the ice shelf has been having</i>

34:53.958 --> 34:56.292
<i>a lot of trouble
with surface melt.</i>

