<i>trying to find a way
to get there.</i>

35:09.940 --> 35:11.941
Hmm, now what?

35:17.414 --> 35:19.015
Get around that

35:32.996 --> 35:35.298
<i>Hey Bill, can you see any
way through?</i>

35:53.818 --> 35:55.552
Yeah, should be all right.

36:06.097 --> 36:08.665
<i>Black Island is
one of the windiest places</i>

36:08.667 --> 36:09.800
<i>on the planet.</i>

